data.description: Dream home! This stunning 4 bed/2 bath home across 2102 sq. ft.  Enjoy view from your lrg backyard with a covered patio. Your inner chef will rejoice with the gorgeous butcher block countertops, dbl oven, gas cooktop, and built-in glass and stainless steel vent fan in the kitchen. The new carpets in all bedrooms and wood look tile in the living areas will elevate your living experience. Enjoy the fireplace or relax in the covered front patio. The new wtr heater and plumbing, and 3-yr-old roof ensure peace of mind. The mudroom/laundry rm has a sink and doggie door. The master opens up to the back patio, features dbl sinks and a rain shower in the bath, and has a walk-in closet. One of the bdrms also opens up to the back patio. The main bath has heat lamps. Home is equipped with solar panels to ensure huge savings on your electric bill. Don't miss out! Must See! Are you a veteran, loan is assumable at 3.875%.
